Localization.Name: ORC-mkV Arms Sakura Sun Edition
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Medium Armor
Damage Reduction: 30%
Temp. Rating: -55 / 85 °C
Radiation Protection: 26400 REM
Radiation Scrub Rate: 145.8 REM/s

Dependable and durable armor never goes out of style. The ORC-mkV from Clark Defense Systems has been a battlefield staple for centuries. This highly regarded medium armor blends composite plating with a special fiber reinforced polymer to provide solid protection and a wide range of movement. The Sakura Sun Edition was made specifically for the company.
